# ShehriSaathi — environment variables
#
# The ONLY secret this app needs. Get a free key (no credit card) at:
#   https://console.groq.com/keys
#
# This single key powers BOTH:
#   - the LLM (llama-3.3-70b-versatile)  -> cited Urdu answers
#   - speech-to-text (whisper-large-v3-turbo) -> Urdu voice input
#
# Copy this file to .env.local and paste your key:
#   cp .env.example .env.local
#
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
